OL,5, The family of a former rugby player is 
OL,6, highlighting the risk of dementia      
OL,7, related to multiple small head         
OL,8, injuries, after he died last year.     
OL,10,FPeter Jones developed early onset      
OL,11,Fdementia in his 50s and died aged 71.  
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination revealed the 
OL,14,Fdementia was caused by repeated blows  
OL,15,Fto the head causing permanent damage.  
OL,17,FHis family has now joined a class      
OL,18,Faction against various sporting bodies 
OL,19,Ffor failing to protect him from the    
OL,20,Frisks caused by concussion.            
